# Walkthrough — Real Interview Window UI

## Changes Made

### 1. [NEW] NLP Communication Analysis Module
[nlp_analysis.py](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/AI-POWERED-INTERVIEW-PREPARATION-COACH/AI_BACKEND/nlp_analysis.py)

- **Filler word detection**: 8+ patterns (um, uh, like, you know, sort of, kind of, basically, actually)
- **Speaking pace (WPM)**: Optimal range 130–160 WPM
- **Fluency metrics**: Vocabulary richness, sentence clarity, average sentence length
- **API**: [analyze_communication(transcript, duration_seconds) → dict](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/AI-POWERED-INTERVIEW-PREPARATION-COACH/AI_BACKEND/nlp_analysis.py#139-219)

### 2. [REWRITE] Frontend — Real Interview Window
[frontend.py](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/AI-POWERED-INTERVIEW-PREPARATION-COACH/frontend_interface/frontend.py)

**Before**: 3-column split layout (Mic | Video | Chat), manual button clicks for everything, only technical scoring.

**After**:
- **2-column interview layout**: Video Coach (left) + Interview Panel (right)
- **Question displayed in styled bubble** with role, difficulty, topic KPIs
- **Inline speech capture**: 🎤 Speak Answer → auto-transcribe → fills answer
- **3D scoring on submit**: Technical (LLM) + Communication (NLP) + Confidence (body language)
- **Live feedback panel** below with score pills, detailed feedback, fillers, WPM
- **End-of-session report**: Aggregated scores, per-question breakdown with expanders, personalized improvement tips
- **Premium dark theme** with glassmorphism, gradients, smooth transitions

