## How to Test

```bash
streamlit run frontend_interface/frontend.py
```

1. Select role → **Start** → verify questions load + TTS reads
2. Take a camera snapshot → **Analyze Posture** → verify body language metrics
3. Click **🎤 Speak Answer** → speak → verify transcript appears
4. Click **✅ Submit** → verify all 3 scores appear (Technical, Communication, Confidence)
5. Click **⏭ Next Q** → new question → repeat
6. Click **⏹ End** → verify results dashboard with all scores and per-question breakdown
